Terraform files for my [blog](https://bentley.link/).

Includes:
- DNS setup for bentley.{link,blog}
- DNS setup for fastmail MX for the same
- s3 buckets for the site, staging site, and logs
- Cloudfront distributions for the site and staging site

Does not include:
- Content for the site; see [here](https://github.com/matthewbentley/blog) for that
- The `bentley_megacert`; that needs to be created (with the proper subdomains)
 outside of tf
